  This program utilizes the @{b}RSA @{ub}cryptographic algorithm which is @{i}copyrighted (©)@{ui} by @{b}MIT@{ub}. Therefore, @{u}it is not allowed@{uu} to use this program and the files it creates inside the @{b}US@{ub} territory. This restriction applies due to the fact that the US goverment treats cryptographic software as @{i}military@{ui} equipment, therefore it prermits its usage by civilians. Everyone that uses cryptographic software inside the US without license, is @{i}prosecuted @{ui}to the maximum extent under the law.

  @{b}@{fg shine}The above restriction applies only to US and nowhere else@{ub}@{fg text}, so the usage of this program - outside US - is safe for everyone. However, this program should not be used for illegal, immoral or other harmfull activities. It was created to protect the private property and to ensure everyone's rights for the freedom of the speech inside our community and the cyberspace.


